  "body": "\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A backyard fire pit instantly transforms outdoor space—perfect for cookouts, winter evenings, and relaxed gatherings. The problem with traditional fire pits is smoke. It irritates the eyes, sticks to clothes, and often forces people to move around the fire instead of enjoying it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A <strong>DIY smokeless fire pit</strong> solves this problem. With proper airflow and secondary combustion, it delivers the warmth and flame you want—without constant smoke. This guide walks you through <strong>how to build a smokeless fire pit at home</strong>, using readily available materials and practical techniques.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://s.vevor.com/QTZBAZ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">https://s.vevor.com/QTZBAZ</a><strong><a href=\"https://s.vevor.com/QTZBAZ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">BUY NOW</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"/images/img-831.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3429\" srcset=\"/images/img-831.webp 1024w, https://championsreviews.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/us_WYRMHKYXPG17PILBIV0_original_img-v2_wood-burning-fire-pit-f5-300x300.webp 300w, https://championsreviews.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/us_WYRMHKYXPG17PILBIV0_original_img-v2_wood-burning-fire-pit-f5-150x150.webp 150w, https://championsreviews.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/us_WYRMHKYXPG17PILBIV0_original_img-v2_wood-burning-fire-pit-f5-768x768.webp 768w, https://championsreviews.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/us_WYRMHKYXPG17PILBIV0_original_img-v2_wood-burning-fire-pit-f5-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://championsreviews.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/us_WYRMHKYXPG17PILBIV0_original_img-v2_wood-burning-fire-pit-f5-1200x1200.webp 1200w, https://championsreviews.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/us_WYRMHKYXPG17PILBIV0_original_im